1134
00:56:53.042 --> 00:56:54.936
Get away!

1135
00:56:55.072 --> 00:56:57.105
- (breathing heavily)
- (beeping slows)

1136
00:57:00.345 --> 00:57:02.143
Jane.

1137
00:57:03.180 --> 00:57:06.250
What Daniel is trying to do
is wrong.

1138
00:57:06.385 --> 00:57:08.823
It's dangerous.

1139
00:57:08.958 --> 00:57:12.252
It would tip the balance in
an already destabilized world.

1140
00:57:13.261 --> 00:57:14.494
JANE:
Yes.

1141
00:57:14.630 --> 00:57:16.731
Jane. could you stop him
if you had to?

1142
00:57:16.867 --> 00:57:19.633
No. No.

1143
00:57:22.635 --> 00:57:25.535
"Father. if you be willing.

1144
00:57:25.671 --> 00:57:28.608
"let this cup pass me by.

1145
00:57:28.743 --> 00:57:31.971
Yet not as I will.
but as you will."

1146
00:57:32.107 --> 00:57:34.483
And what did Christ say next?

1147
00:57:36.179 --> 00:57:38.553
"By my will.
thine will be done."

1148
00:57:39.590 --> 00:57:43.091
If the moment comes.
I'll be with you.

1149
00:57:43.226 --> 00:57:45.088
and you'll act. Jane.

1150
00:57:45.223 --> 00:57:48.827
out of love for Daniel.
out of love for the human race.

1151
00:57:52.126 --> 00:57:53.832
Now look around the room.

1152
00:57:55.004 --> 00:57:56.395
Slowly.

1153
00:57:59.901 --> 00:58:01.103
Left to right.

1154
00:58:04.377 --> 00:58:05.811
Stop there.

1155
00:58:07.214 --> 00:58:08.682
Get up.

1156
00:58:12.519 --> 00:58:13.647
Walk to the counter.

1157
00:58:13.782 --> 00:58:15.821
