1158
00:58:21.694 --> 00:58:23.565
Pull out the chopping knife.

1159
00:58:30.735 --> 00:58:31.934
Give me your phone!

1160
00:58:32.070 --> 00:58:33.698
- Oh. shit! What?
- Give me your phone.

1161
00:58:33.834 --> 00:58:35.203
Jackson. come on. come on.
come on. give me your phone.

1162
00:58:35.338 --> 00:58:36.510
Give me your phone.
Give me your phone.

1163
00:58:36.645 --> 00:58:38.041
- Okay. hold on. hold on!
- Come on!

1164
00:58:38.176 --> 00:58:38.804
