1170
00:58:48.883 --> 00:58:49.851
Who is this?

1171
00:58:49.986 --> 00:58:51.555
Do not go back to the house.

1172
00:58:51.691 --> 00:58:53.921
Scan-Scanlon dove on Jane.

1173
00:58:54.056 --> 00:58:55.520
Does that mean anything to you?

1174
00:58:55.656 --> 00:58:57.359
- Okay. Give me your...
- Look. they found you.

1175
00:58:57.495 --> 00:58:59.201
I don't know who you are.
and I don't know who they are.

1176
00:58:59.336 --> 00:59:00.900
but they're gonna kill you.

1177
00:59:01.036 --> 00:59:02.361
- Give me the phone.
- They are gonna kill you both.

1178
00:59:02.497 --> 00:59:04.201
- Give me my phone!
- You need to leave.

1179
00:59:04.337 --> 00:59:05.572
Give me my phone. Maggie!
Give me my phone! Oh. my God!

1180
00:59:05.708 --> 00:59:07.338
I'm so done
with your crazy shit!

1181
00:59:07.474 --> 00:59:09.006
