1195
01:01:03.593 --> 01:01:05.186
What am I doing?
What am I doing?

1196
01:01:05.322 --> 01:01:07.594
What am I doing?
What am I doing? Okay.

1197
01:01:07.729 --> 01:01:09.326
What am I doing?
What am I doing?

1198
01:01:09.461 --> 01:01:11.197
- What am I doing?
What am I doing?
- Hold it!

1199
01:01:11.332 --> 01:01:13.167
- What am I doing? What am I
doing? What am I doing?
