1202
01:01:16.605 --> 01:01:18.305
AGENT:
Shoot the tires!

1203
01:01:18.441 --> 01:01:19.635
It's him! It's him!

1204
01:01:19.770 --> 01:01:21.067
Watch out!

1205
01:01:21.202 --> 01:01:22.968
(indistinct shouting)

1206
01:01:23.103 --> 01:01:25.538
