1207
01:01:26.648 --> 01:01:28.211
AGENT:
Go for the tires!

1208
01:01:30.143 --> 01:01:32.886
(panting)

1209
01:01:34.455 --> 01:01:36.021
Oh. shit.

1210
01:01:37.088 --> 01:01:39.387
(engines revving in distance)

1211
01:01:47.469 --> 01:01:49.595
(tires squealing)

1212
01:01:53.236 --> 01:01:54.733
What am I doing?
What am I doing?

1213
01:01:54.868 --> 01:01:57.035
What am I doing?
What am I doing? What am I...

1214
01:01:57.170 --> 01:01:58.912
What am I doing?

1215
01:02:03.179 --> 01:02:04.348
- Hands up!
- Stop!

1216
01:02:04.484 --> 01:02:05.549
Get him!

1217
01:02:05.685 --> 01:02:07.018
Get out! Now!

1218
01:02:07.154 --> 01:02:08.082
