- (engine revving)

1219
01:02:08.217 --> 01:02:09.414
Let me see your hands! Hands up!

1220
01:02:09.550 --> 01:02:11.221
- Hands up!
- (tires squealing)

1221
01:02:23.867 --> 01:02:25.906
