1226
01:02:59.968 --> 01:03:01.007
Jane!

1227
01:03:02.069 --> 01:03:03.339
Jane.

1228
01:03:04.711 --> 01:03:06.243
(engines revving)

1229
01:03:13.886 --> 01:03:16.583
