1243
01:03:51.757 --> 01:03:52.861
Get down!

1244
01:03:57.866 --> 01:03:59.730
Whoa. whoa. whoa. whoa. whoa!

1245
01:03:59.865 --> 01:04:01.201
(tires squealing)

1246
01:04:01.337 --> 01:04:02.365
(gasps)

1247
01:04:07.802 --> 01:04:10.301
No. no. no. no. no. no.
no. no. no. no. no.

1248
01:04:10.437 --> 01:04:11.803
No. no. no. no. no.

1249
01:04:11.938 --> 01:04:13.776
Look. Jane. it wasn't you.
It wasn't you.

1250
01:04:13.911 --> 01:04:15.141
It was Scanlon.

1251
01:04:15.277 --> 01:04:16.609
The device. The device.

1252
01:04:16.745 --> 01:04:18.986
Roll him on three.
One. two. three. go.

1253
01:04:24.518 --> 01:04:26.191
